#

Maple-Glazed Brussels Sprouts and Bacon

$12.99
300 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Tags:

VegetableSide DishSavorySweet

Description

Savory-sweet Brussels sprouts caramelized with maple and crispy bacon—perfectly balanced and utterly delicious!

Ingredients

  • Brussels sprouts: 1 lb
  • Bacon: 6 slices
  • Maple syrup: 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
